/*
This is the defs for the fixed "elements" table: 
table < elements >
 No. Type  Description
[ 1]  *I   30003			TDFentry
[ 2]   A   30005 [20]		Element Name
[ 3]   I   30013			Default Width
[ 4]   A   30007 [30]		Heading
[ 5]   A   30011 [20]		Range
[ 6]   A   30012 [1]		Required? (Y/N)

Example:
-> l elements w 2 = rec_no
[ 1]  *I  30003                : 29963
[ 2]   A  30005                : Rec_No
[ 3]   I  30013                : 10
[ 4]   A  30007                : Rec No
[ 5]   A  30011                :
[ 6]   A  30012                : n

*/

